name: Latest issue of Rock-A-Rolla - no.47 (UK Customers)
description:
Order the latest issue of Rock-A-Rolla! 

On the cover: Godspeed You! Black Emperor’s Efrim Menuck talks the return of Thee Silver Mt. Zion Memorial Orchestra!

Inside: Top 50 albums of 2013, Melt-Banana, Secret Chiefs 3, Beastmilk, Culted, Celeste, Solar Halos, 25 years of Rise Above Records!

Plus: massive live reviews section, including Damnation Festival, Amplifest, Queens Of The Stone Age, Vista Chino, Lee Ranaldo & The Dust, Thurston Moore, Om, The Ocean, Baroness, Alice In Chains, Wolf Eyes, Kadavar! Plus: the latest album reviews, and much more!

This option is for UK Customers and price includes all postage and packing costs
